<h1 class="glitch" data-text="Cards">Cards</h1>
<p><a href="https://github.com/asafonov/cards.apk" target="_blank">Cards</a> is a small collection of card games I made just for fun, because I enjoy making games. You can play on your Android device or in <a href="https://asafonov.org/cards" target="blank">a browser</a></p>
